:"TAKE FUNCTION AND PREDICTION INPUTS
Input "Y1: ",Str1
Input "Y2: ",Str2
Input "PREDICTION: ",X
:"CONVERT STRING INPUTS TO FUNCTIONS
Str1→Y₁
Str2→Y₂
:"X IS CURRENT VALUE IN ITERATION, L IS PREVIOUS, M IS 2ND PREVIOUS
X-1→L
0→M
:"D IS DIFFERENCE, USED TO TRACK WHETHER GETTING CLOSER
abs(Y₂-Y₁)→D
:"I IS ONLY TO TRACK WHETHER FIRST TIME RUNNING
0→I

:"LABEL USED FOR ITERATION/LOOP
Lbl Z
Disp X
If Y₂=Y₁:Then
:"ANSWER HAS BEEN FOUND
:Disp "X is equal to",X
:Stop
Else
:If X>L:Then
:"IF WE HAD INCREASED LAST TIME
::L→M
::X→L
:"IF WE'VE GOTTEN CLOSER, INCREASE AGAIN
::X-1+2*(abs(Y₂-Y₁)<D)→X
::abs(Y₂-Y₁)→D
:Else
:"IF WE HAD DECREASED LAST TIME
::L→M
::X→L
:"IF WE'VE GOTTEN CLOSER, DECREASE AGAIN
::X+1-2*(abs(Y₂-Y₁)<D)→X
::abs(Y₂-Y₁)→D
:End
End
:"IF WE WERE AT THE SAME VALUE TWO ITERATIONS AGO
:"I>1 CASE IS TO MAKE SURE THIS DOESN'T HAPPEN AT BEGINNING
If M=X and I>1:Then
:Disp "X is between",L,"and",X
:Stop
End
I+1→I
Goto Z